UPDATE experiences SET user_reviews = '[{"name":"Marco R.","country":"🇮🇹 Italy","rating":5,"date":"2026-01-05","text":"What an adrenaline rush! The instructor was professional and safety-focused, but we still had an absolute blast. Can''t wait to do it again!","source":"getyourguide","verified":true},{"name":"Katrine H.","country":"🇩🇰 Denmark","rating":5,"date":"2025-12-23","text":"Incredible experience! The water was surprisingly warm and the views of the cliffs from the water were spectacular. Don''t miss this.","source":"viator","verified":true},{"name":"David H.","country":"🇺🇸 United States","rating":5,"date":"2025-12-12","text":"One of the highlights of our Lisbon trip. Well-organized, fun, and great value for money. Would absolutely do it again.","source":"viator","verified":true},{"name":"Rafael O.","country":"🇧🇷 Brazil","rating":5,"date":"2025-12-02","text":"A memorable experience that we''ll be talking about for years. Professional, fun, and uniquely Portuguese. Don''t hesitate!","source":"getyourguide","verified":true},{"name":"Lucas F.","country":"🇧🇷 Brazil","rating":5,"date":"2025-11-20","text":"The scenery was breathtaking and the activity was so much fun. Perfect mix of adventure and natural beauty. Highly recommend!","source":"viator","verified":true},{"name":"Fatima A.","country":"🇲🇦 Morocco","rating":5,"date":"2025-11-15","text":"Worth every penny. The combination of sport and stunning scenery was unbeatable. We came back tired but exhilarated.","source":"viator","verified":true},{"name":"Charlotte D.","country":"🇧🇪 Belgium","rating":5,"date":"2025-11-15","text":"Amazing day out. The instructors were fun and knowledgeable. We saw sea caves, marine life, and had the time of our lives.","source":"getyourguide","verified":true},{"name":"Patrick O.","country":"🇮🇪 Ireland","rating":5,"date":"2025-07-09","text":"Highly recommend! Well-run, engaging, and a lot of fun. One of the best things we did during our stay in Portugal.","source":"viator","verified":