UPDATE experiences SET user_reviews = '[{"name":"Jan V.","country":"🇳🇱 Netherlands","rating":5,"date":"2025-12-20","text":"Loved learning the secrets behind Portuguese cuisine. The dessert was the surprise hit — never would have thought to combine those flavors.","source":"getyourguide","verified":true},{"name":"Helena R.","country":"🇵🇱 Poland","rating":5,"date":"2025-12-16","text":"We had an amazing time. The attention to detail was impressive and the staff clearly care about delivering a great experience.","source":"viator","verified":true},{"name":"Camila S.","country":"🇧🇷 Brazil","rating":4,"date":"2025-11-28","text":"Good class overall. Some dishes were more complex than others, but the chef guided us through everything patiently. Tasty results!","source":"viator","verified":true},{"name":"Thomas M.","country":"🇩🇪 Germany","rating":5,"date":"2025-11-09","text":"Booked this for my mom''s birthday and she was thrilled. Intimate, personal, and delicious. The chef even wrote a recipe card for us.","source":"getyourguide","verified":true},{"name":"Lisa B.","country":"🇩🇪 Germany","rating":5,"date":"2025-10-07","text":"Such a fun and delicious experience! We learned to make pastel de nata from scratch. The chef was patient and hilarious. 10/10!","source":"viator","verified":true},{"name":"Ashley P.","country":"🇺🇸 United States","rating":5,"date":"2025-09-28","text":"We brought the whole family including our 12-year-old — everyone had a blast. The cataplana was incredible. Best souvenir: the recipes!","source":"viator","verified":true},{"name":"Antoine D.","country":"🇫🇷 France","rating":5,"date":"2025-06-10","text":"Hands-on from start to finish. We cooked a full Portuguese meal and ate it together. The recipes work — I''ve already made them at home!","source":"getyourguide","verified":true},{"name":"Martin P.","country":"🇨🇿 Czech Republic","rating":5,"date":"2025-05-10","text":"Brilliant! Everything ran smoothly and the quality was exceptional. This is exactly the kin